#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_digital.rst:2
msgid "Digital Propagation"
msgstr "Propagación digital"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_digital.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation` "
"functional propagates a digital quantum circuit through the backend. "
"Because it subclasses "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`, any "
"symbolic parameters exposed by the underlying "
":class:`~qilisdk.digital.circuit.Circuit` can be queried or updated "
"through helper methods such as "
":meth:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable.get_parameter_names`."
msgstr ""
"El funcional :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation` "
"propaga un circuito cuántico digital a través del backend. Al ser una "
"subclase de :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`, "
"cualquier parámetro simbólico expuesto por el "
":class:`~qilisdk.digital.circuit.Circuit` subyacente puede consultarse o "
"actualizarse mediante métodos auxiliares como "
":meth:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable.get_parameter_names`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_digital.rst:10
msgid ""
"Measurement details such as the number of shots are specified separately "
"via readout objects passed to "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`."
msgstr ""
"Los detalles de medición, como el número de shots, se especifican por "
"separado mediante objetos de lectura que se pasan a "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`."

